8 SUMMARY
99 This bill amends the notice requirements to the public regarding state contracts and
1100 grants. The bill requires additional notice to the public when a state contract is renewed for
1111 a 3rd renewal period or when a contract with a total value greater than $1,000,000 is
1122 renewed.
